title: "Daily Release publish step runs prepublishOnly post-tag: align npm publish with --ignore-scripts"
description: "Fleet alignment after pm-ts-starter run 27448995157 failed at npm publish: without --ignore-scripts, prepublishOnly re-runs changelog:check AFTER the release tag exists, where the pending-version window suppression (issue #41 in this repo) renders the zero-padded tag heading and the check can never pass. Siblings already publish with --ignore-scripts; full validation still runs pre-tag."
